summary:
- **Index Removal:** Spartan Resources Limited (ASX: SPR) to be removed from the S&P/ASX 200 Index due to acquisition by Ramelius Resources Limited (ASX: RMS).  
- **Effective Date:** Removal will occur prior to market open on **Wednesday, 23 July 2025**.  
- **Replacement:** Infratil Limited (ASX: IFT) will replace Spartan in the S&P/ASX 200 on the same date.  

*No other material information identified.*
